item.title: BFKit - A collection of useful Swift classes, structs, and extensions
item.description: Fabrizio Brancati has created a cool Swift library which provides a collection of useful Swift classes, structs, and extensions. It's aim is to help developers crate apps faster. There is lots here including many extensions to Foundation, UIKit, and WatchKit classes.
